---
import MainLayout from '@/layouts/MainLayout.astro';
import Header from '@/components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '@/components/Footer.astro';
---
<MainLayout title="404 - 页面未找到 | 秒派科技" description="您访问的页面不存在，请返回秒派科技官网首页。">
  <Header />
  <main class="flex min-h-screen items-center justify-center bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-50 to-white px-4 pt-16 dark:from-slate-950 dark:to-slate-900">
    <section class="max-w-xl text-center">
      <p class="text-sm font-black tracking-[0.4em] text-emerald-700">404</p>
      <h1 class="mt-4 text-4xl font-black text-slate-950 dark:text-white md:text-6xl">页面未找到</h1>
      <p class="mt-5 text-lg leading-8 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">当前地址可能已失效，或页面已被移动。您可以返回首页继续了解小程序与后台管理系统方案。</p>
      <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col justify-center gap-3 sm:flex-row">
        <a href="/" class="rounded-2xl bg-emerald-700 px-7 py-3 font-extrabold text-white transition hover:bg-emerald-800">返回首页</a>
        <a href="/download" class="rounded-2xl border border-emerald-200 bg-white px-7 py-3 font-extrabold text-emerald-700 transition hover:bg-emerald-50 dark:border-slate-700 dark:bg-slate-900 dark:text-emerald-300">预约演示</a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</MainLayout>